<p>A true kaiju spectacle. The Ultraman Blazar: Spectacle Live show at <a href="https://nitter.rawbit.ninja/NY_Comic_Con" title="New York Comic Con">@NY_Comic_Con</a> was an incredible showcase of fantastic choreography &amp; tokusatsu magic. Seeing Ultraman Blazar &amp; Earth Garon fight monsters on stage made me feel like a little kid again. Loved it. <a href="https://nitter.rawbit.ninja/TsuburayaGlobal" title="ULTRAMAN Global">@TsuburayaGlobal</a></p>
